{
  "stem": "9725.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And of course, you know, we wore uniforms, and all that, and that was until I was 15.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, the war broke out just when I was just 15.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was not a problem, because, you know, I-- I grew up in-- even though, you know, in an observant Jewish family, but my parents had many non-Jewish friends.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my Nana-- my nanny was the one who brought me up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was Catholic.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, I-- you know, she used to go to church every day.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as a small child, I used to go with her every day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and so there was never any problem.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean-- you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was taught to respect her religion, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And on Christmas we used to go to her house and I used to have help trim the tree and all that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we had Hannukah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there was great respect on both sides.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, in-- in school, we used to have a rabbi coming to the convent to give us Jewish instructions, for which of course our parents paid separately.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was not too much of a problem.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Tell me a little bit more about your relationship with your-- with Nana.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My Nana?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Apparently that dated back a long time in my family, and Nana used to tell me that story-- that she was married to a postman in our town.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one day-- and he died very early.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a terrible fire broke out, which destroyed all her belongings.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the only thing that she had is her-- that was not destroyed was her husband's postman's jacket, which was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she knew my grandmother slightly.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
